: 994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throw inthe sixth-fastest women's 800m time in historyat the London Diamond League meet just before the Olympics and the expectations are suddenly stratospheric.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1057, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9998691996528982, \"rank\": 0.00011914885183162816, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9997089490291002, \"rank\": 0.0002911357060525055, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Diamond_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"historyat\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"the expectations\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson said: \\\"I feel like this is going to be my proper Olympic experience.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my proper Olympic experience\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last time with Covid, they did an amazing job putting it on.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"an amazing job\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But now, with the crowd, I think it's going to be a proper experience, so I am really excited.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"a proper experience\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It really did change my life.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics is something that resonates with the majority of the public, so it's just really special to perform well there.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"the majority\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a different pressure this time.\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different pressure\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very upcoming, that position I was in, I will never have that again.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that position\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The freedom of being there for the experience and it did not really matter what I did.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The freedom\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew what I could do.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now, we are three years later, I think I am a better athlete than I was then but now there is that expectation.\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better athlete\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"that expectation\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have medalled every year now so it's a case of can we do it again?\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a case\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can we go one better?\\\"\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her cause has been helped by Tokyo gold medallist and 2022 world champion Athing Mu, who is three months younger than Hodgkinson,missing out at the US Olympic trials.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2013, \"end\": 2018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7806867431023279, \"rank\": 0.2805156543688761, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2058, \"end\": 2067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Athing Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\"}, {\"begin\": 2102, \"end\": 2112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9435478550155949, \"rank\": 0.0593746259695423, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her cause\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"2022 world champion\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2057}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where Hodgkinson was able to skip the 800m at the UK Championships, having already clinched a place in Paris, the Americans have a cutthroat selection policy where only the top three at their trials can go to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995143298, \"rank\": 4.857261408834328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 800m\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"the UK Championships\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2218}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2251}, {\"ngram\": \"the Americans\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"a cutthroat selection policy\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"their trials\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So when Mu was clipped and fell during the race, her Olympic hopes evaporated.\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2384, \"end\": 2386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.999798998890498, \"rank\": 0.0002010415109015266, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic hopes\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than count her blessings, Hodgkinson is disappointed to miss out on the chance to take on her rival, while also admitting that suffering a similar fate is something of a preoccupation.\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2488, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her blessings\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"her rival\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar fate\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"a preoccupation\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"Unfortunately Athing is not going to be in Paris this year.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2702, \"end\": 2707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995143298, \"rank\": 4.857261408834328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athing\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very gutted about that.\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it was me, I'd be devastated, it's not nice to see that happen.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though she's not there, it's still so hard to achieve, it's just one less person to worry about.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just one less person\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's going to be difficult but it's the Olympic Games, anything can happen.\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2993, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2971}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 2981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With races like that, I have had my heels clipped a few times.\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"my heels\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It makes you wary that just because you are the best, that does not mean that it can not happen to you.\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was very unfortunate, so you just have to keep your wits about you.\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your wits\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"800m and 1500m are two of the messy races for that, people getting on top of each other, piling up, so you just have to stay out of trouble.\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"800m\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"the messy races\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3275}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"trouble\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes you can not control it, so you just have to hope the luck is on your side.\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the luck\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"your side\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It does cross your mind sometimes, what if I fall over?\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your mind\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But hopefully not!\\\"\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In many ways, it appears that Hodgkinson's progress has been almost all highs, settling for the odd silver medal rather than gold, notwithstanding.\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3567, \"end\": 3577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many ways\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3549}, {\"ngram\": \"almost all highs\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"the odd silver medal\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3649}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 22-year-old admits that the aftermath of her Olympic debut was not easy and took a while to come to terms with.\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3804, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"But the 22-year-old admits\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3711}, {\"ngram\": \"the aftermath\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic debut\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3751}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"I have shown how mentally strong I can be.\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Tokyo, the Olympic comedown is a real thing.\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3867, \"end\": 3872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7806867431023279, \"rank\": 0.2805156543688761, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic comedown\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3894}, {\"ngram\": \"a real thing\", \"from\": 3898, \"to\": 3910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was quite tough, being so young and having so many aspects of my life change.\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3994, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many aspects\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 3975}, {\"ngram\": \"my life change\", \"from\": 3979, \"to\": 3993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not go to university anymore, I went full-time pro.\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"university\", \"from\": 4011, \"to\": 4021}, {\"ngram\": \"full-time pro\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I moved out, got my own place, all these changes you go through anyway.\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own place\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4082}, {\"ngram\": \"all these changes\", \"from\": 4084, \"to\": 4101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then you think I have got to do what I did last year again, for a whole year, finding that motivation.\", \"from\": 4126, \"to\": 4233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a whole year\", \"from\": 4195, \"to\": 4207}, {\"ngram\": \"that motivation\", \"from\": 4217, \"to\": 4232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I now know this time around that I will be better equipped to handle that.\", \"from\": 4234, \"to\": 4308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also want to enjoy it, I am back to really enjoying it again.\", \"from\": 4309, \"to\": 4372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I get to that final and give it my all, I will be happy.\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After Tokyo, there was no pressure on me.\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4441, \"end\": 4446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7806867431023279, \"rank\": 0.2805156543688761, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no pressure\", \"from\": 4458, \"to\": 4469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only thing I did not want was to be a one-hit wonder, who just got it right then.\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only thing\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4491}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-hit wonder\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to prove not just to myself but to everyone else that I could be a multiple medallist.\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4607, \"to\": 4615}, {\"ngram\": \"a multiple medallist\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here we are, three years later, with a lot more medals so it's good fun!\\\"\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4732, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot more medals\", \"from\": 4696, \"to\": 4713}, {\"ngram\": \"good fun\", \"from\": 4722, \"to\": 4730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pressure might have changed but Hodgkinson's potential remains sky-high.\", \"from\": 4734, \"to\": 4810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4770, \"end\": 4780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.93943